%% Arquitetura Geral - Tech Challenge Fase 04
%% This diagram represents the high-level architecture of the solution.
%% Language: English

graph TD
    subgraph Cloud Environment
        direction TB
        ServerlessFunctions["Serverless Functions\n(Feedback, Notification, Report)"]
        ManagedDB["Managed Database\n(Postgres)"]
        Monitoring["Monitoring & Alerts"]
        Governance["Access Governance & Security"]
    end

    User["User (Student)"] -->|Submit Feedback| ServerlessFunctions
    ServerlessFunctions -->|Store Feedback| ManagedDB
    ServerlessFunctions -->|Send Notification| NotificationService["Notification Service"]
    ServerlessFunctions -->|Generate Weekly Report| ReportService["Report Service"]
    Monitoring -.-> ServerlessFunctions
    Governance -.-> ServerlessFunctions
    Governance -.-> ManagedDB

    NotificationService -.->|Urgent Notification| User
    ReportService -.->|Weekly Report| Admin["Admin/Analyst"]
